flowchart TD
  Maintainer[Maintainer updates browser UI] --> AppShell[src/app/App.jsx app shell]
  AppShell --> Model[src/app/app-model.jsx route and view helpers]
  AppShell --> Auth[src/app/routes/AuthRoute.jsx]
  AppShell --> Create[src/app/routes/CreateTaskRoute.jsx]
  AppShell --> Workspace[src/app/routes/TaskWorkspaceRoute.jsx]
  AppShell --> Detail[src/app/routes/TaskDetailRoute.jsx]
  AppShell --> Admin[src/app/routes/AdminUsersRoute.jsx]

  Workspace --> OwnerHelpers[src/app/task-owner.mjs]
  Detail --> DetailFeature[src/features/task-detail adapters and shell]
  Create --> CreationFeature[src/features/task-creation adapter and schema]

  Lint[npm run lint] --> RepoLint[scripts/lint-repo.js]
  Lint --> BrowserReadability[scripts/check-browser-source-readability.js]
  BrowserReadability --> StrictScope[src/app and src/features production files]
  StrictScope --> RequiredVerification[npm run typecheck, npm run test:ui, npm run test:browser, npm test]
